maintext:
INDIANAPOLIS (AP) _ The winning numbers in Thursday evening’s drawing of the Indiana Lottery’s “Quick Draw Evening” game were:
06-07-12-17-19-23-26-34-41-42-43-46-50-56-64-65-66-71-72-74, BE: 7
(six, seven, twelve, seventeen, nineteen, twenty-three, twenty-six, thirty-four, forty-one, forty-two, forty-three, forty-six, fifty, fifty-six, sixty-four, sixty-five, sixty-six, seventy-one, seventy-two, seventy-four; BE: seven)
